```
@searchlog =
    EXTRACT UserId int,
            Start DateTime,
            Region string,
            Query string,
            Duration int?,
            Urls string,
            ClickedUrls string
    FROM "/input/SearchLog.tsv"
    USING Extractors.Tsv();

OUTPUT @searchlog 
    TO "/output/SearchLog-first-u-sql.csv"
    USING Outputters.Csv();
```
